Company Overview of CNH Partners, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
CNH Partners, LLC is a privately owned hedge fund manager. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It also caters to investment companies and UCITS. The firm manages separate client focused portfolios. It also launches and manages hedge fund for its clients. The firm invests in public equity and hedging markets. It employs various arbitrage strategies to make its investments. The firm employs fundamental analysis to make its investments.  CNH Partners, LLC was founded in 2001 and is based in Greenwich, Connecticut.


Two Greenwich Plaza3rd FloorGreenwich, CT 06830United StatesFounded in 2001



Phone: 203-742-3600

Fax: 203-742-3100








