How do I update this listing?




                                             CNH Partners is based out of Greenwich. CNH Partners is a hedge fund  with  11-25 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $6,492,534,149 (Form ADV from 2017-03-31).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $8,865,290,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 23.77%. CNH Partners's largest holding is Novell Inc. with shares held of 99,914,000.   WhaleWisdom has at least 34 13Fs and  62 13D/G filings in our database for CNH Partners. 
                                           














